                <h4>Jewish Language</h4>

    
              <p>0-6 credits of a Jewish language.  Each Joint Honours student will complete at least one Jewish language at the advanced level of instruction. A student who can demonstrate competence in a Jewish language may be permitted to substitute other courses for all or part of the language requirement.</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
