              HIST 207 Jewish History: 400 B.C.E. to 1000 (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-27398" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
