      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Lea Fima (Fall)                  </p>

    
          <ul class="catalog-notes">
              <li>Students must register for both JWST 320D1 and JWST 320D2.</li>
              <li>No credit will be given for this course unless both JWST 320D1 and JWST 320D2 are successfully completed in consecutive terms</li>
              <li>JWST 320D1 and JWST 320D2 together are equivalent to JWST 320</li>
